summary: Removes nearly all snow patches in the College of Winterhold exterior, and removes the snow from the models.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-s2qNEDCn4mo/UNzj-pNYEAI/AAAAAAAAAo4/m34KKqctedk/s800/dmcline.png[/img][/center]

Removes nearly all snow patches in the College of Winterhold exterior, and removes the snow from the models. Used in screenshots, but not part of the mod:  [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/7484] Sexy Winterhold College by horrorview[/url].
author: dmcthunder999
